The Wednesday views of the Cybertruck were perhaps the best look at the vehicle we‚Äôve had thus far, as plenty of photos from the company‚Äôs Investor Event earlier this week were shared. Tesla seems to have landed on a final design for an updated Yoke steering wheel, as well as improvements to the vehicle‚Äôs interior, like folding rear seats for additional space.

